Class DeployViewSchemasCommand

    Command, UndoableCommand

    public class DeployViewSchemasCommand
extends AbstractResourceCommand
    So for a given view-schema resource, after it's been processed, we'll check for a (name)-views folder in the view-schemas folder. If it exists, we'll process each file in the directory. We don't need to do anything on undeploy fortunately.
